relation with respect to\nthe dimensional variables. Further evaluation of classification accuracy with\nrespect to the reference, a BERT based speech representation model, shows that\nthe proposed method is comparable to the reference method in classifying\nspecific emotion classes at a much lower complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 16:14:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
