ues. Hence, the findings of this work advance the knowledge on the design of\nCFS and provides both, for researchers a theoretical contribution to reason\nabout design principles and a guideline to managers and decision makers for\ndesigning software artefacts efficiently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 05:59:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 08:13:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
