ng to an overall positive\nhalf-mass bias. Our work provides a quantitative reference for selecting the\nbest features to discriminate the DS of galaxy clusters in both simulations and\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 06:30:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 00:19:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-14"}
