g Sn and were evaluated\nusing first-principles molecular dynamics; their Li-ion conductivities at room\ntemperature were found to be comparable with those of garnet-type Li-ion\nconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 09:23:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 05:58:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 07:50:07 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 22 Aug 2022 06:36:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-23"}
