 observer was synthesized and\nthe results of computer modeling illustrating the achievement of a given goal\nwere presented. The main difference from the results published earlier in $[2]$\nis the new assumption that the linear a time-varing system contains not only\nunknown parameters in the state matrix, but also the matrix (vector) for\ncontrol contains unknown constant coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 09:32:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
