l simulations using state-of-the-art\nmethods, allowing one to simulate even heterogeneous electrodes. Moreover, it\nallows unveiling more rigorously how electrode curvature affects the\ncapacitance with the one-dimensional correction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 12:03:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 May 2022 08:25:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2022 15:27:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-29"}
