ance improvements on various frameworks and datasets from 30 hours to\n14.3k hours. The proposed method achieves state-of-the-art (SOTA) results on\nAishell-1 (CER 4.10%) and Aishell-2 (CER 5.02%) datasets. Code is released.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 14:32:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Apr 2022 03:47:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2022 03:37:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-24"}
