 would be better when the campaign\nlength keeps longer and with high cadence. As a result, the capability of\nMuztagh-Ata 1.93m telescope allows it to join the network of TDSL\nobservatories. It will enrich the database for strongly lensed quasar\nobservations and make more precise measurements of time delays, especially\nconsidering the unique coordinate of the site.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Mar 2022 15:38:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
